#encoding: utf-8

Feature: Comparison3 - Full-Bound Range

  Scenario: [1] Handling numerical ranges 1
    Given an empty graph
    And having executed:
      """
      UNWIND [1, 2, 3] AS i
      CREATE ({num: i})
      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (n)
      WHERE 1 < n.num < 3
      RETURN n.num
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | n.num |
      | 2     |
    And no side effects

